      • marshal

        public static Ad marshal(java.lang.Object object)
        Marshal an object into an ad. This method checks if the type of object is registered as a special marshalling case, and if so delegates to the marshalling handler. Otherwise, it marshals the object field-wise.
        Parameters:
        object - the object to marshal into a new Ad
        Returns:
        An ad representation of the object, or null if object is null.
